{"tid":1469650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停止互屌，集中宣傳818百萬人遊行，好嗎？","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:25:43.000Z","uid":114802,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f16fe6ed4c94aca84dc1bc16bd7924e8bbd383f","tid":1469650,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"大家都係手足<br />\n見到大家互相指責個心唔好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明大家係同呼同吸 向同一個目標努力<br />\n琴晚機場件事係處理得唔夠好<br />\n但係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">不完美，可接受，可改善</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明白不割蓆唔等於唔可以批評<br />\n唔阻都阻咗，捉鬼都捉咗，過去咪由佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冷處理，好嗎？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都好嬲，但可以留住呢份情緒去集中宣傳818遊行嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有4日，但一個宣傳post都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfb同社交媒體都冇咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事後檢討係需要，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好蓋過宣傳</span></span><br />\n上次616嘅宣傳係舖天蓋地<br />\n今次民怨咁沸騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要谷到百萬人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預想今日警方同政府記者會一定係強烈譴責譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後又一班人反駁反駁<br />\n跟著又佔曬所有媒體嘅討論<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劇本黎</span></strong></span><br />\n咪正中港共下懷，想你班人割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再聚焦琴晚機場，全力谷行818</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818百萬人大遊行<br />\n黑警還眼<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"5551c068dede760a29b0b4c1d6c8283699881070","tid":1469650,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185a802410710518c25ca1228b48d2efb0347cef","tid":1469650,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">818百萬人大遊行<br />\n黑警還眼<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8612c42f8fae60b6a4b091ac26ea395cef73f5bb","tid":1469650,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"